      1          /*
      2           * DHT11 single-wire driver on CC2530 P2.0.
      3           *
      4           * The board provides an external 10k pull-up. Follow the reference start
      5           * sequence: drive low >=18 ms, drive high for 20~40 us, then switch to input
      6           * to sample the sensor response. Timing assumes the system is already running
      7           * on the existing 32 MHz XOSC configuration used by the project.
      8           */
